data.description: Charming, well-maintained home in the heart of a beautiful, quiet neighborhood. This home has been well cared for and provides plenty of options for comfortable living space. New concrete patio in tranquil, private back yard is perfect for relaxing and/or entertaining. Brand new fence, new kitchen flooring and freshly painted cabinets, new garage door opener, and newer bathroom finishes make this home pop! Office space on lower level can be easily converted to third bedroom. ***Property was previously listed and sold as three bedroom but third "bedroom" would be non-conforming in the basement. Lower level office area could easily be converted to third conforming bedroom with addition of wall and closet.***
